HEADWORD: Commensality
<hw>Com`men*sal"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Fellowship at
table; the act or practice of eating at the same table.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Promiscuous <xex>commensality</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
